 https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Cave-Carnage-Tour-1392x884.jpg 1392w, https://www.nme.com/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/Nick-Cave-Carnage-Tour-1068x678.jpg 1068w" sizes="(max-width: 2000px) 100vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/nick-cave">尼克·凯夫 (Nick Cave)</a>最近在芝加哥的音乐会上首次推出了一首全新歌曲 - 请观看下面的完整视频。</p><ul><li><strong>阅读更多： <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-is-currently-finishing-the-new-bad-seeds-album-3472170">Nick Cave 目前正在“完成”新的 Bad Seeds 专辑</a></strong></li></ul><p>9 月 29 日，凯夫在芝加哥表演了一首亲密的钢琴民谣，随后回应了一位粉丝在他的时事通讯中询问这首歌的问题。这位澳大利亚音乐家一直在慢慢地公布新的 Bad Seeds 专辑的细节，今年五月初透露， <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-on-the-new-bad-seeds-album-and-the-chances-of-more-from-grinderman-3449133">这张音乐“非常有趣”，而且“一直与众不同”</a> 。</p><p>在<a href="https://www.theredhandfiles.com/" target="_blank" rel="noopener"><em>《红手档案》</em></a>第 255 期中，凯夫详细阐述了他在亚历山德拉宫表演的《安乐死》的创作过程，以及一首他称之为《To Be Found》的新歌。</p><p> “当我与 The Bad Seeds 一起制作专辑时，我偶尔会独自在钢琴上录制一首歌，”他写道。 “从风格上来说，这些歌曲通常处于新唱片之外，它们通常是碎片化的东西，形状是圆形的，唱起来轻柔，不引人注目且不成形。乐队对他们的喜爱程度很低，而且他们的实力也不足以与更大、更气势磅礴的歌曲竞争——因此他们往往会被半途而废。”</p><p> “当我回听录音时，我会遇到其中一两首被遗忘在某个被遗忘的角落里的歌曲，我会发现自己暗自被它们朴素的可爱所感动，”他继续说道。 “因此，我对他们变得非常依恋。我在阿什维尔和克利夫兰演奏的《安乐死》是我在《骷髅树》时期写的一首歌曲，是一个完美的例子——当时被忽视了，现在它已成为我的最爱之一。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="安乐死 - 白痴祈祷：尼克·凯夫独自在亚历山德拉宫" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/1r55tjbmBQM?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p>凯夫说，《To Be Found》是“另一首这样的歌曲”。最初表演时没有歌名，凯夫继续说道：“情感简单、轻声细语，这首歌甚至无法说出它的名字，但它仍然是一首特殊的歌曲，充满了未指明的情感冲击力，演奏起来非常愉快。我想我会把这首歌命名为“To Be Found”。” </p><p><iframe loading="lazy" title="Untitled, Unreleased Song - Nick Cave (Live at Auditorium Theater, Chicago, 9.29.23)" width="696" height="392" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/gEwbZaLCytk?feature=oembed" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen></iframe></p><p> The Bad Seeds last released music with 2019&#39;s &#39; <a href="https://www.nme.com/reviews/nick-cave-ghosteen-review-2553785">Ghosteen</a> &#39;; our five-star review asserted it was “one of the most devastatingly accurate accounts of grief that you&#39;ll ever listen to. Yet it&#39;s also, astoundingly, one of the most comforting.”</p><p> Cave has previously <a href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/nick-cave-starts-work-on-new-bad-seeds-album-and-shares-early-lyrics-3376286">shared snippets of lyrics he has written for the upcoming record</a> ; in January, he described the process as “a nasty, punishing, baggy-eyed business”, and said he had started writing on New Year&#39;s Day. “It is now January 6. Nearly a week has passed and I&#39;ve written a few things but they aren&#39;t very good, or maybe they are, it&#39;s difficult to tell,” he wrote in <em>The Red Hand Files</em> .</p><p> The post <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com/news/music/watch-nick-cave-debut-new-song-to-be-found-in-chicago-3510845">Watch Nick Cave debut new song &#39;To Be Found&#39; in Chicago</a> appeared first on <a rel="nofollow" href="https://www.nme.com">NME</a> .</p> ;
